> On Mon, Jan 10, 2005 at 05:25:38PM +0100, Luca Falavigna wrote:
> > This simple patch adds a new file in /proc, listing every kprobe which
> > is currently registered in the kernel. This patch is checked against
> > kernel 2.6.10
> 
